  "body": "#### System information\n\nGeth version: `1.4.11-stable`\nOS & Version: Ubuntu Linux 64bit\nCommit hash : N/A\n#### Expected behaviour\n\nGeth runs, syncs and eats normal amount of RAM\n#### Actual behaviour\n\nGeth runs, starts to sync and gets killed by OOM killer because it goes over 2GB of RAM usage real fast.\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\n\nRun geth with no options is enough\n#### Backtrace\n\nMemory output from geth before getting killed\n[mem.out.gz](https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/files/478990/mem.out.gz)\n",
